                <p>Victoria is the capital city of British Columbia and is located at the eastern edge of the massive Vancouver Island, which sits off the coast of Canada. Due to its location, Victoria can only be reached by plane or ferry, which departs from both Vancouver and Port Angeles, Washington.</p>
