        <div id="british-columbia-greater-victoria-attractions" class="tabcontent">
            <div class="tabcontent-text-container">
                <p>North of Victoria are the Butchart Gardens, a gorgeous collection of well-manicured themed gardens with vibrantly colored flowers and plants, as well as mesmerizing fountains. West of Victoria along the Strait of Juan de Fuca are many beautiful beaches surrounded by tall dense forests. You can reach these scenic beaches via lush forested hiking trails.</p>
